    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/7998136/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_8970145748245410275.png",
                "id": "talent92129",
                "key": "往生秘傳槍法",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "往生秘傳槍法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>本角色附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">彼岸蝶舞</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">彼岸蝶舞</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p>所附屬角色造成的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>變為<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>，且角色造成的<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色進行重擊時：</span>目標角色附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">血梅香</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/7998136/786741b419f21d96999ca7832a738088_6042048705773087517.png",
                "id": "talent39743",
                "key": "蝶引來生",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "蝶引來生"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>，治療自身2點。如果本角色生命值不多於6，則造成的傷害和治療各+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/7998136/3fd894c657ed5975d54c71d665e6bcc9_5401044040053500627.png",
                "id": "talent61659",
                "key": "安神秘法",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "安神秘法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著火元素，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，生成回合結束時造成1點火元素傷害的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[燃燒烈焰]</span>（可用次數1，最多疊加到2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/7998136/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_3237028706466809780.png",
                "key": "火元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">重擊</span></strong></p><p>我方行動開始前，如果元素骰總數為偶數，則進行的「普通攻擊」將被視為「重擊」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">血梅香</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>對所附屬角色造成1點<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合結束階段，<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/7998136/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6344279524494955298.png",
                "key": "規則解釋",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "規則解釋"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
